:"2019-09-03T16:13:07.000Z","msg":"2335 香港獨媒直播員話太子站B出口，警察打傷市民，有人失去意識，急救近半小時，傷者都未有反應。<br />\n<br />\n2348 救護員將傷者送往醫院救治，期間為傷者戴上氧氣罩，但未見氣袋有漲過。（呼吸弱／昏迷）<br />\n<br />\n0005  有線直播訪問FA人員，FA 講述以下情況。<br />\n1. 一開始傷者被六個防暴警察壓落地，FA見傷者失去活動能力，上前急救，發現傷左左後頸有腫脹，<span style=\"color: red;\">懷疑頸椎／背脊骨受傷</span>。<br />\n2. 警察要求FA留底身份證同FA證作記錄，FA急救期間要求除去傷者衣物，<span style=\"color: red;\">警方以保留證物為理因拒絕</span>，經FA說服後允許剪去一半衣物，但<span style=\"color: red;\">急救期間一直未有解開傷者手扣</span>。<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">傷者出現氣促情況，有透唔到氣既徵狀，到後期失去意識</span>。<br />\n4. 10分鐘後，救護員到場，<span style=\"color: red;\">要求警方解開傷者手扣方能進行急救，警員才解開手扣</span>，急救時間約二十分鐘，救護員將傷者帶往醫院。"},{"pid":"ab44474fdcccfabe6b5148ff7c734b8d1f9a6bd4","tid":1536330,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:13:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dc3b84b25a10e15a0cd883d8ab5d75c2dda43822","tid":1536330,"uid":155180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5218943302212d95c9133ef28ace43f56356fc","tid":1536330,"uid":80139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3128e0e5399b3a3a318ff623a78d8f905845ee8","tid":1536330,"uid":69646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:13:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bec9611d7c11a48afe714343b7ac15f6d0db4607","tid":1536330,"uid":155180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a943fb7a12686ad33d2633196988957fc84a28c","tid":1536330,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a807334f5e5f371725