rge;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警 還命</span></span>"},{"pid":"4635e0ff6646171a34636a14680d20190057e447","tid":1536330,"uid":69505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:31:11.000Z","msg":"唔好有事"},{"pid":"ffe08a1c718746443bda17b11c63a15a0f91ceef","tid":1536330,"uid":74586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:31:53.000Z","msg":"我地唔好再得把口<br />\n我都好驚，但對住呢班狗，我地唔可以再怕，我地一齊打狗，一齊升級好嗎<br />\n<br />\n我地一齊以來既升級只有打爛啲死物，但佢地就不斷合理化佢既武力，仲一直向我地既頭部攻擊甚至恐襲。下次，再有啲狗追人，我地企硬唔好再走了。應承手足，呢一世都唔好原諒班狗，好嗎"},{"pid":"6d20df847cb3f0cd0490637a9d9c2fd61941474f","tid":1536330,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:31:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">車左去廣華！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"5286c80ed3347be35020bbbd00f076c9d6bcbcc5","tid":1536330,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"994e569b5f6e6b2c991fdf2a9c2210a3fe7a0cf1","tid":1536330,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:33:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1412878685473594/videos/1610379849098897/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1412878685473594%2Fvideos%2F1610379849098897%2F&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=a21f93c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1412878685473594/videos/1610379849098897/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:32:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">太子現場FA指：<br />\n-黑警要FA交出身分證明同FA證先比救，故意延誤急救<br />\n-傷者有氣促，FA建議解手扣抒緩，黑警唔比；建議除衫，黑警又話係證物唔比，最後bargain一輪只比剪開一半，又故意將人道急救置於執法之下<br />\n-傷者頸椎腫 有血 應有骨折傷勢 氣促，昏迷至離開上白車<br />\n-黑警圍住走，唔比任何人跟車，或者問去邊</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7f2349ab937fa265319f39cee5d9008ff97ca299","tid":1536330,"uid":206613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:33:14.000Z","msg":"Back up<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"}]}